    </paragraph>

    <paragraph>
      Well, if you start thinking about a generic solution that would benefit
      the community at large, you’ll soon realize that it’s necessarily going to
      be surprisingly complex and nuanced:
    </paragraph>

    <paragraph>
      1) it’s difficult to agree even on the most basic terms. ‘simplistic’,
