    <paragraph>
      railsnew.io falls into the ‘something else’ category: it’s a GUI to
      _generate the command line_. Once it’s generated, you just need to
      copy&paste and run it. No need for further customization, extra flags or
      interactive mode: the generated command line captures _everything you want
      your app to be_.
    </paragraph>

    <paragraph>
